the general area that I didn't even notice Dantrazz had arrived. <br>
<br>
&quot;Uh, Hi&quot; covered in bear blood I bowed before Dantrazz as he offered to guide me somewhere else to hunt. &quot;Sure, I think it would be good to leave the bears, I'm starting to see them in my sleep... WAIT I never thought of it before... Dream Walker bears, no wonder they were able to catch me as I woke. They were homing in on my dreams!&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;Riiiiight... follow me Nag.&quot; Dantrazz commanded, so I did. we wnet back to Neriak where Dantrazz stopped at the bank and we ran into Tyshalae. I could even read her thoughts like a book... Dantrazz = candy for Tyshalae. Candy + Tyshalae = Sugar Rush. Sugar Rush + Tyshalae = many frightened people.<br>
<br>
