<br>
Before I found a group I decided to explore alone a bit... not really the best idea I've ever had. I attacked a dry-bones... didn't know it could spit fire. Damn thing hurt me quite a bit before I decided to fear it and attack while it ran. Thing ran right to it's mummy! After I defeated both dry bones and mummy  and lost my pet skellie I decided to sit at the docks for a bit to recover. <p><img align=center src="http://www3.sympatico.ca/bmckella/nagsig.jpg">

